book:
FFTW (Fastest Fourier Transformer in the West)
FFTW


 &reftitle.intro;


  PHP binding for FFTW (Fastest Fourier Transformer in the West) Library for computing the discrete
  Fourier transform (DFT) in one or more dimensions, of arbitrary input size, and of both real and 
  complex data (as well as of even/odd data, i.e. the discrete cosine/sine transforms or DCT/DST).



